snippet.textDisplay:
The amount of effort you guys are putting into each of your videos is insane. And let me tell you, the great composition, Vocals, Instrument playing, the vibe, the feel truly complements your hard work and second to none in this entire world. Every Sunday you guys are making us feel proud and giving us something unique and amazing.
Magical and everlasting voice of forever young the great Sajjad Ali, wow! His style of singing is as if he is just cruising with ease but give it a try and you will learn it's not easy to sing such song with such ease. What a legend!!!
And what a pleasant and feel good vocals of Farheen, whoever decided to get this sung by her is a genius which I have no doubt you all are!
Bravo on another one to go on my playlist of eternity from CS.
